            <td>@ConclusionTypeName</td>
            <td>@InputCode</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
    <tbody id="EmptyConclusionTypeQuickQueryDataTemplete">
        <tr>
            <td colspan="3" style="text-align:center;">未找到相关结论词分类，请重新输入...&nbsp;</td>
